metadata.name: Crazy
metadata.description:
Bruce Lee used to say that water can flow or it can crash. A woman's strength is like water - soft but powerful.
She is Crazy, because she doesn't care what other people think of her, she just does her job and doesn't follow all the rules so she doesn't miss out on the fun!
5824 x 7280
Oil on canvas 50x80 cm POP ART
